Subject: [PATCH] pin Go toolchain to the version vendored in tinytree

Upstream tracks the latest toolchain; the monorepo pins a specific version so
all imported services build reproducibly. Candidate for upstreaming once acme
adopts toolchain pinning.

---
diff --git a/go.mod b/go.mod
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/go.mod
+++ b/go.mod
@@ -1,6 +1,8 @@
 module github.com/acme/backend

 go 1.21
+
+toolchain go1.21.6

 require (
 	github.com/spf13/cobra v1.8.0
